With KDE Support (Recommended)
==============================
1. mkdir build
2. cd build
3. cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`kde4-config --prefix`
4. make
5. sudo make install


Qt-Only
=======
1. mkdir build
2. cd build
3. cmake .. -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DWANT_KDE_SUPPORT=NO
4. make
5. sudo make install
